    @NextUpdate
public class SemiMixtureREM
extends AbstractMixtureREM
implements net.hudup.core.alg.DuplicatableAlg, net.hudup.core.alg.NoteAlg
    This class implements the semi-mixture regression model. If there are 2 partial models and dual mode is true, this semi-mixture regression model becomes dual regression model.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
